  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of this activity is to employ one local communicator and one local value chain coach in Ghana, Burkina Faso, Togo, Sao Tome and Principe. Currently, local communicators have already been employed in all four project countries. Value chain coaches were also employed in Sao Tome, Burkina Faso and Ghana. In Togo, the value chain coach function is also fulfilled by the two communicators.</narrative>
